metadata.name: COLORIST #1
metadata.description: The planet PALETTE filled with intense colors, romantic and psychedelic. The native inhabitants of the planet are CU (CURIOUS) and IN (INSIGHT). The CU collect Color Energy to provide raw materials for the planet's production. While the IN have the ability to inspire and create. CU collects Color Energy and pays some Color Energy for Planetary Governance Bureau to obtain collect privileges. IN promotes the development of PALETTE with inventions and creations in the laboratory, and can receive rewards from the Planetary Governance Bureau.
